    <div class="description">
        <h1 class="maintitle">Who we are</h1>
        <hr class="index_ruler">
        <p>This website was created by three Portuguese foreigner souls that, despite all odds, have chosen from their hearts to make Finland feel like home. Coming from different backgrounds, having faced very personal immigration journeys, and having developed unique relationships to Finland, we decided to unite in putting this project together because… why not?</p>
        <p>Find out a little more about us below and in case you have nice ideas for this project, let us know how we can make it better!</p>
    </div>

